File: Water dripping from a tap.Â Flickr.com/Lazellion JOHANNESBURG - Johannesburg residents linked to the Commando and Crown Garden systems have little to no water. Their taps have been going dry for some time now because of infrastructure problems at Rand Water's Vereeniging purification works. Johannesburg Water says both Hursthill reservoirs are critically low to empty. The Crown Gardens reservoir is also low.